The people have 7 different jobs:  analyst, coach, doctor, fisherman, journalist, police-officer, social-worker
There are 7 different favourite colors: chestnut, light-blue, black, aquamarine, yellow, coral, pink
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person eating orange##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is the person who likes pink##1
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 5. the social-worker is on the left of the analyst##1
 6. the doctor is in the middle##1
 7. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 8. the fisherman is on the far left##1
 9. the police-officer is the person who likes yellow##1
10. the person eating corn is on the right of the journalist##1
11. the person who likes black is the social-worker##1
12. the person eating peach is on the left of the coach##1
13. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who likes black##1
14. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating banana##1
15. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |       2        |    3    |    4    |     5      |       6       |     7      |
